## Built with

- [Kuzu](https://kuzudb.com/) — embedded graph database
- [Typer](https://typer.tiangolo.com/) — CLI framework
- [Rich](https://rich.readthedocs.io/) — terminal UI
- [MCP Python SDK](https://github.com/anthropics/mcp) — agent protocol
- [Watchdog](https://python-watchdog.readthedocs.io/) — file system watcher
- [Anthropic Python SDK](https://github.com/anthropics/anthropic-sdk-python) — PRD summarization

